data.description: Enjoy your mornings on the wrap-around porch of this beautifully landscaped 4 bed/3 bath home in Farmington. Home features hard floors in main living areas, vaulted ceiling, 2 dining areas, sunroom, large laundry room, plenty of storage room, built-in, gas fireplace and many wonderful details. Located in North Clubhouse Estates and less than 10 minutes from restaurants, shopping, businesses, I-49 and more.
